Interface IViewImage

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AWTImage

    public interface IViewImage
    Abstract interface for an image. A view should cast this to what it expects.

      • getImage

        java.lang.Object getImage()
        Get the image.
        Returns:
        This method returns the image in the format that the current view should expect. The view must cast the object that is returned to what it expects. *Check the cast*
